我认为他现在什么也不会说
I don't think he's gonna say anything now.

768
00:52:16,059 --> 00:52:17,939
你必须去找摩西和博格斯
You've got to find Moses and Boggs.

769
00:52:19,979 --> 00:52:22,098
别担心 我正在路上
Don't wory. I'm on the trail.

770
00:52:22,099 --> 00:52:25,859
伦敦
LONDON

771
00:52:27,099 --> 00:52:30,019
在右边 你看到的是出名的伦敦塔
On your right, you see the famous Tower of London.

772
00:52:30,899 --> 00:52:33,059
我们会穿过塔底下
And shortly, we'll be passing under the Tower Bridge.

773
00:52:38,899 --> 00:52:40,098
一个堡垒
It's a fortress.

774
00:52:40,099 --> 00:52:43,058
它是秘密关押罪犯的监狱
It's an asylum for the criminally insane.

775
00:52:43,059 --> 00:52:44,938
他在ICE里面
He's in the ICE unit.

776
00:52:44,939 --> 00:52:47,059
那是MI6 A级安保地点
That's an MI6 Alpha Level secure facility...

777
00:52:47,899 --> 00:52:49,219
深藏在那座大楼中
buried deep within that building.

778
00:52:49,939 --> 00:52:51,979
就像监狱中的监狱
It's like a prison within a prison.

779
00:52:54,019 --> 00:52:56,059
我们要怎么进去
How are we gonna get in there?

780
00:53:00,019 --> 00:53:02,098
他想要我的头
She wants my head!

781
00:53:02,099 --> 00:53:03,938
这是天主教的阴谋
It's a Papist plot.

782
00:53:03,939 --> 00:53:07,938
那个苏格兰贱人皇后 他想要我的头
It's that bitch May Queen of Scots. She wants my head.

783
00:53:07,939 --> 00:53:09,098
你在干什么 不
What are you doing? No!

784
00:53:09,099 --> 00:53:11,059
给我叫塞西尔 我才是苏格兰皇后
Get me Cecil. I'm the Queen of England!

785
00:53:11,979 --> 00:53:13,978
不要带我去城堡
Don't take me to the Tower!

786
00:53:13,979 --> 00:53:16,099
我会砍下你的头的 婊子
I'll have your head for this, you bitch!

787
00:53:16,899 --> 00:53:19,059
不 不
No! No!

788
00:53:20,979 --> 00:53:25,019
头戴王冠可不简单啊
"Uneasy lies the head that wears the crown."

789
00:53:25,979 --> 00:53:29,018
他们所有的人都想要反抗我
They're plotting against me. All of them.

790
00:53:29,019 --> 00:53:30,939
这才是个好皇后
There's a good queen.

791
00:53:32,099 --> 00:53:35,059
别说了 老妖怪
Stuff it, you old bat.

792
00:53:35,899 --> 00:53:37,099
谢了
Thank you.

793
00:53:38,019 --> 00:53:40,979
如果不介意 别再叫我老妖怪了
Not so much the "old", if you don't mind.

794
00:53:49,899 --> 00:53:51,058
我觉得这个很不错
I think it was really good.

795
00:53:51,059 --> 00:53:53,059
我以为在引导Bette Davis呢
I thought I was channeling Bette Davis.

796
00:53:55,059 --> 00:53:58,059
早安 琼斯医生想要看一下17号患者
Good morning. Dr. Jones to see prisoner number 17, please.

797
00:53:58,860 --> 00:54:00,098
琼斯医生 来自MI6的吗
Dr. Jones? Are you with MI6?

798
00:54:00,099 --> 00:54:01,978
当然 但不再是了
Certainly, not anymore.

799
00:54:01,979 --> 00:54:04,059
电脑表单上没有你的名字
I don't seem to have you on my list.

800
00:54:05,979 --> 00:54:09,019
这东西不好使用 为什么
Bloody thing's not working. Why's that?

801
00:54:11,019 --> 00:54:12,059
你应该使用...
You're supposed to use.

802
00:54:12,899 --> 00:54:14,059
趴在地板上 很好
Lay down on the ground.

803
00:54:17,979 --> 00:54:21,059
121病房 就是那里
Number 121. There it is.

804
00:54:28,939 --> 00:54:31,019
法兰克
Frank!

805
00:54:46,939 --> 00:54:49,018
你们是谁 参观的吗 找谁呢
Who are you? You're visitors? Who are you looking for?

806
00:54:49,019 --> 00:54:51,019
我们喜欢参观者 不是吗 伙伴们
We love having visitors, don't we, fellas?

807
00:54:51,939 --> 00:54:53,979
贝利教授
Dr. Bailey?

808
00:54:54,939 --> 00:54:56,059
贝利教授
Doctor Bailey?

809
00:54:56,899 --> 00:54:58,939
是啊 不然还会有谁呢
Yes. Who did you expect to find here?

810
00:55:04,979 --> 00:55:05,978
教授
Sir...

811
00:55:05,979 --> 00:55:07,098
怎么
What?

812
00:55:07,099 --> 00:55:09,058
我看到你死了
I saw you die.

813
00:55:09,059 --> 00:55:10,938
看到我死了 他是谁
Saw me die? Who is he?

814
00:55:10,939 --> 00:55:12,098
法兰克
Frank?

815
00:55:12,099 --> 00:55:16,098
法兰克・摩西 我亲爱的朋友 你好吗
Frank Moses, my dear fellow! How are you, old sport?

816
00:55:16,099 --> 00:55:18,098
很高兴见到你 欢迎你来
So glad to see you. So glad you came by.

817
00:55:18,099 --> 00:55:20,018
我们期待很久了 不是吗
We've been expecting you. Haven't we, fellas?

818
00:55:20,019 --> 00:55:21,098
天啊 你怎么这么老了
My God, why are you so old?

819
00:55:21,099 --> 00:55:22,059
老天啊
Good lord!

820
00:55:22,939 --> 00:55:23,099
教授
Sir...

821
00:55:23,100 --> 00:55:25,018
什么
What?

822
00:55:25,019 --> 00:55:28,058
你已经被关32年了
You've been locked up here for 32 years.

823
00:55:28,059 --> 00:55:31,098
来吧 法兰克 开什么玩笑 玩一下
Frankie, you've gotta be kidding me. Come on, put 'em up.

824
00:55:31,099 --> 00:55:34,058
32年 怎么可能 你叫什么名字
32 years. How exraordinay. Who are you?

825
00:55:34,059 --> 00:55:35,019
维多利亚
Victoria.

826
00:55:35,860 --> 00:55:38,938
维多利亚 你应该看看这个 列宁的 "国家与革命"
Victoria! You should read this. Lenin. " State and Revolution."

827
00:55:38,939 --> 00:55:41,058
快乐的时光 斯大林肯定会搞砸的
Jolly good time. Stalin got it wrong, of course.

828
00:55:41,059 --> 00:55:44,018
我们要去哪里呢 法兰克 歌剧院吗
Where are we going, Frank? Are you taking us to the opera?

829
00:55:44,019 --> 00:55:46,098
我们要去哪里 我们都喜欢歌剧 不是吗
Is that where we're going? We love the opera, don't we, fellas?

830
00:55:46,099 --> 00:55:48,938
有香槟和草莓的歌剧院
The opera and the champagne and the strawberries all round.

831
00:55:48,939 --> 00:55:50,098
抱歉 亲爱的 再请问你的名字
sorry, my dear, what is your name again?

832
00:55:50,099 --> 00:55:51,058
维多利亚
Victoria.

833
00:55:51,059 --> 00:55:54,938
抱歉 这是药物作用 影响我的记忆
sorry, it's the drugs they're feeding me, it's my short term memory.

834
00:55:54,939 --> 00:55:59,059
一种让我平静而又无害的东西
Something that's meant to keep us peaceful or harmless!

835
00:55:59,899 --> 00:56:03,059
反正就在附近 但我又不知道在哪里
Anmay, it's around here somewhere, but I don't know where.

836
00:56:04,099 --> 00:56:07,098
贝利教授 我们需要你的帮助
Dr. Bailey, we need your help.

837
00:56:07,099 --> 00:56:09,099
你记得"暗影行动"吗
Do you remember Nightshade?

838
00:56:09,939 --> 00:56:14,018
抱歉 我在找烟斗和圣克里斯托弗奖章
I'm looking for my pipe and my St. Christopher medallion.

839
00:56:14,019 --> 00:56:16,099
那些年轻人把它给别人了 都是些小孩
Boys gave it to someone. They were little boys.

840
00:56:16,899 --> 00:56:19,059
大概跑到哪里去了
And now it's gone somehow.

841
00:56:29,939 --> 00:56:31,979
喔 糟糕
Oh shit!

842
00:56:33,059 --> 00:56:34,978
法兰克 我在这里
Hey, Frankie, I'm over here.

843
00:56:34,979 --> 00:56:36,898
我找到了 一直在我的口袋里
I found it. It was in my pocket the whole time.

844
00:56:36,899 --> 00:56:38,978
尽管我找不到烟斗了 还好在这里
I couldn't find my damn pipe, though. But here it is.

845
00:56:38,979 --> 00:56:41,059
抱歉 亲爱的 你刚才问我什么
sorry, my dear, what was the question you asked me?

846
00:56:41,899 --> 00:56:43,059
你记得"暗影行动"吗
Do you remember Nightshade?

847
00:56:43,899 --> 00:56:46,018
我记得那是一种炸弹
Vaguely. It was some kind of a bomb, I believe.

848
00:56:46,019 --> 00:56:49,938
有人正在找它 想要使用它
People are looking for that weapon. People who want to use it.

849
00:56:49,939 --> 00:56:52,058
亲爱的 我了解 相信我
Oh dear. Yes, I do understand of course. Believe me.

850
00:56:52,059 --> 00:56:55,098
我为美国制造了很多东西
But I made many things for the Americans and...

851
00:56:55,099 --> 00:56:57,099
"暗影行动"是最吓人的杰作
Nightshade turned out to be a bit of a nightmare.

852
00:56:57,899 --> 00:56:59,098
与众不同 又非常危险
It was quite different. Turned out to be too dangerous.

853
00:56:59,099 --> 00:57:01,938
所以他们自然要把我关在这里
So naturally, they had to lock me up in this place.

854
00:57:01,939 --> 00:57:04,018
即使他们对我做了这些事后 我觉得这很正常
And after what they did to me, I think it's perfectly natural...

855
00:57:04,019 --> 00:57:07,059
我警告过他们要滚远点
I tell them all to go F off!

856
00:57:08,099 --> 00:57:11,018
MI6想制造贝利死亡的谎言
MI6 tried to fake Bailey's death?

857
00:57:11,019 --> 00:57:12,059
为什么 他们想隐瞒什么
Why? What are they hiding?

858
00:57:12,899 --> 00:57:15,180
你得走了 他们发现你了
You're gonna have to go. You're gonna have to go find out.

859
00:57:16,979 --> 00:57:19,098
他们想杀了我的
You know they're gonna Ty and kill me.

860
00:57:19,099 --> 00:57:20,098
到俄国再找你
I'll call you from Russia.

861
00:57:20,099 --> 00:57:22,899
维护7号桥
Maintenance to Bridge 7.

862
00:57:23,939 --> 00:57:25,979
安全系统出现紧急状况
We got a breach in Maximum Security.

863
00:57:34,899 --> 00:57:35,979
保全
Secure!

864
00:57:41,059 --> 00:57:42,938
什么事那么重要
What's so important?

865
00:57:42,939 --> 00:57:46,098
我刚从MI6得到消息 爱德华贝利还活着 并已经逃走了
I just heard from my source at MI6 that Edward Bailey's alive and on the run.

866
00:57:46,099 --> 00:57:47,019
这不可能
That's not possible.

867
00:57:47,899 --> 00:57:50,018
这比想像中的麻烦还大
This is bigger than a rogue General and his unexploded ordinance.

868
00:57:50,019 --> 00:57:51,058
我还有什么不知道的
What don't I know?

869
00:57:51,059 --> 00:57:52,938
游戏改变了
The game has changed.

870
00:57:52,939 --> 00:57:55,058
贝利知道的事情太危险了
The things Bailey knows are too dangerous.

871
00:57:55,059 --> 00:57:59,099
如果贝利或者暗影行动落入恐怖份子 将有数万人会丧生
If Bailey or Nightshade fall into terrorist hands, millions will die.

872
00:58:00,059 --> 00:58:02,018
喔 天啊 这是真的
Holy shit, it's real.

873
00:58:02,019 --> 00:58:05,058
除非我们销毁它，那个武器正在莫斯科中心地区
Unless we secure it, that weapon's going off in the middle of Moscow.

874
00:58:05,059 --> 00:58:07,979
这就是我们最好的应急措施
Right now, that's our best case scenario.

875
00:58:14,939 --> 00:58:16,939
俄罗斯
RUSSIA

876
00:58:39,019 --> 00:58:41,859
伙计们
Guys?

877
00:58:59,099 --> 00:59:01,979
欢迎 我的朋友们
Welcome, my friends.

878
00:59:04,059 --> 00:59:09,018
传言是真的 你还活着
So, it is true. You're alive.

879
00:59:09,019 --> 00:59:13,059
告诉我 是谁操控的
Tell me, then, where is this device?

880
00:59:13,979 --> 00:59:15,899
谁
Who?

881
00:59:18,939 --> 00:59:20,899
我们在努力
Work in progress.

882
00:59:22,899 --> 00:59:25,058
我从来没有想过
I never thought I'd be smuggling...

883
00:59:25,059 --> 00:59:29,058
带法兰克・摩西到俄罗斯中心地区去
Frank Moses into the heart of Mother Russia.

884
00:59:29,059 --> 00:59:31,098
我也是
Me, neither.

885
00:59:31,099 --> 00:59:34,058
在我忘记前 这里有点小东西
Before I forget. A little something.

886
00:59:34,059 --> 00:59:38,018
如果你被抓了或韩抓了你
If you are caught or Han catches you...

887
00:59:38,019 --> 00:59:43,019
服药自杀是最好的选择
suicide pill is a much better option than what you face.

888
00:59:44,899 --> 00:59:48,059
就算死 也会死得很漂亮
You die with Russian smile on.

889
00:59:50,860 --> 00:59:52,979
祝好运
Good luck.

890
00:59:54,019 --> 00:59:55,058
贝利教授
Mr. Bailey.

891
00:59:55,059 --> 00:59:56,058
法兰克
Yes, Frank?

892
00:59:56,059 --> 01:00:01,018
有什么方式可以告诉我们核武器在哪里
Is there any way you could tell us where you hid the nuclear weapon?

893
01:00:01,019 --> 01:00:04,979
这些堡垒 可真是漂亮啊
Look at all those cows. They're beautiful.

894
01:00:05,899 --> 01:00:07,859
堡垒
Yeah.

895
01:00:08,979 --> 01:00:10,979
母牛
Cows?

896
01:00:15,979 --> 01:00:18,899
嗨！
Hi! Yoo hoo!

897
01:00:21,939 --> 01:00:24,019
情况不妙
That's not good.

898
01:00:24,899 --> 01:00:26,979
莫斯科
MOSCOW

899
01:00:36,979 --> 01:00:39,899
我们被跟踪了 法兰克
We have eyes on, Frank.

900
01:00:59,019 --> 01:01:00,939
我的飞机在哪里
Where's my plane?

901
01:01:02,979 --> 01:01:05,018
他们雇我来杀你
They paid me to kill you.

902
01:01:05,019 --> 01:01:07,059
没有说要保留全尸
They didn't say I had to do it all at once.

903
01:01:07,899 --> 01:01:08,978
别动
FREEZE

904
01:01:08,979 --> 01:01:09,939
把手放头上
HANDS ON YOUR HEAD

905
01:01:22,939 --> 01:01:25,058
波士奇呼叫 这里有警察受伤
THIS IS OFFICER BOESKY. OFFICER DOWN

906
01:01:25,059 --> 01:01:27,939
我们需要医生
WE NEED MEDICALASSISTANCE

907
01:01:35,019 --> 01:01:38,098
别动 把手放头上
FREEZE, HANDS ON YOUR HEAD

908
01:01:38,099 --> 01:01:39,939
他怎么了
What's wrong with him?

909
01:02:36,939 --> 01:02:38,059
哇
Wow.

910
01:02:38,899 --> 01:02:40,098
这是什么地方
What is this place?

911
01:02:40,099 --> 01:02:41,979
我第一个安全屋
My first safe house.

912
01:02:43,099 --> 01:02:47,059
邻家女孩 是从1984年开始的
Untouched, since 1984.

913
01:02:54,059 --> 01:02:56,058
河豚毒
Fugu poison?

914
01:02:56,059 --> 01:02:59,938
那可是剧毒
Fugu poison is deadly stuff. Terrible death.

915
01:02:59,939 --> 01:03:03,099
看到了吗 XKG毒气 我发明的
This little gizmo? XKG gas. I invented it.

916
01:03:04,059 --> 01:03:07,018
我们想在61年刺杀古巴总统卡斯楚
We tried to take out old Fidel Castro in '61 in Cuba.

917
01:03:07,019 --> 01:03:09,018
但是没有奏效
That didn't work though.

918
01:03:09,019 --> 01:03:10,019
选一个吧 法兰克
Any tea, Frank?

919
01:03:10,860 --> 01:03:12,099
为什么韩那么讨厌你
Why does Han hate you so much?

920
01:03:12,899 --> 01:03:14,059
从小时候起他就讨厌我
Not enough hugs as a child.

921
01:03:16,059 --> 01:03:21,098
法兰克盗取了国家的机密
Frank framed him for stealing state secrets.

922
01:03:21,099 --> 01:03:25,059
然后从一个优秀情报员
So he went from being a highly decorated counter intel officer...

923
01:03:25,899 --> 01:03:28,059
变成可怕的杀手
to being a pariah.

924
01:03:28,939 --> 01:03:30,978
最讽刺的是 法兰克
What's ironic is that Frank...

925
01:03:30,979 --> 01:03:35,058
总在刺杀时出现了些状况
actually created the circumstances for his own death.

926
01:03:35,059 --> 01:03:37,018
很戏剧性
It's poetic.

927
01:03:37,019 --> 01:03:38,059
我还没有死
I ain't dead yet.

928
01:03:46,899 --> 01:03:50,098
你在吃那东西
Should you eat that?

929
01:03:50,099 --> 01:03:52,098
安全吗
Is that safe?

930
01:03:52,099 --> 01:03:56,859
它还是在  过期之前
It's before they had that, you know, "sell by" date stuff.

931
01:03:59,899 --> 01:04:02,058
所以你见过卡斯楚了
Did you get to meet Castro?

932
01:04:02,059 --> 01:04:03,059
谁
Who?

933
01:04:03,939 --> 01:04:05,058
你见过卡斯楚了
Did you get to meet Castro?

934
01:04:05,059 --> 01:04:07,300
当然 在甘乃迪死后的二星期
Yes, I did. About 2 weeks after Kennedy was assassinated.

935
01:04:07,939 --> 01:04:09,018
顺便说一下 法兰克
Talking of which, Frank...

936
01:04:09,019 --> 01:04:12,019
我开始记起来我是谁了
I'm starting to remember more and more who I am...

937
01:04:12,860 --> 01:04:14,018
我以前干什么的 还有我制造的武器
and who I was and the weapons I made.

938
01:04:14,019 --> 01:04:16,058
天啊 太神奇了
My God, it really is amazing.

939
01:04:16,059 --> 01:04:19,978
MI6的人都是好人 上帝保佑他们
How efficiently those boys from MI6, God bless 'em...

940
01:04:19,979 --> 01:04:22,180
但他们确实遗弃了我们 不是吗 老兄
But they really do throw us away. Don't they, old sport?

941
01:04:22,899 --> 01:04:25,058
我们年龄大了 大概吧
When we're no longer convenient, I suppose.

942
01:04:25,059 --> 01:04:27,419
好像我们没有把最好的时光献给它
As though we'd never given them the best years of our lives.

943
01:04:27,939 --> 01:04:28,979
真是个天大的笑话
Bit of a ioke, really.

944
01:04:29,979 --> 01:04:31,939
没错 真奇怪
Yes, vey strange.

945
01:04:33,059 --> 01:04:36,059
你记得"暗影行动"在哪里吗
Do you remember where Nightshade is?

946
01:04:36,979 --> 01:04:38,098
抱歉 亲爱的
I'm sorry, my dear?

947
01:04:38,099 --> 01:04:41,018
你记得"暗影行动"在哪里吗
Do you remember where Nightshade is?

948
01:04:41,019 --> 01:04:42,059
当然记得
Oh, yes.

949
01:04:43,939 --> 01:04:45,859
好像是穿过这里
This feels right.

950
01:04:48,899 --> 01:04:51,099
我来过这里 我肯定
It's around here somewhere. I'm sure this time.

951
01:04:51,979 --> 01:04:54,058
一切都变不一样了
Eveything looks different completely.

952
01:04:54,059 --> 01:04:56,018
可能是穿过这里
Maybe it's over here.

953
01:04:56,019 --> 01:04:56,978
一小时了
It's been hours.

954
01:04:56,979 --> 01:04:58,058
就是这里
Yeah, this is it.

955
01:04:58,059 --> 01:05:00,058
我们到了
Here we are.

956
01:05:00,059 --> 01:05:02,939
你觉得这事和吉米周有什么关系
How are those Jimmy Choos working out for you?

957
01:05:03,899 --> 01:05:05,018
入口在上面
The entrance is up there.

958
01:05:05,019 --> 01:05:06,098
约翰爸爸
PAPA JOHN'S

959
01:05:06,099 --> 01:05:07,978
谁是约翰爸爸
Who's Papa John?

960
01:05:07,979 --> 01:05:09,058
刚听到的
It's new.

961
01:05:09,059 --> 01:05:10,059
去哪里的入口
Entrance to what?

962
01:05:10,899 --> 01:05:12,938
穿过古陵寝的秘密通道
Secret tunnels through the old catacombs.

963
01:05:12,939 --> 01:05:14,978
这曾是布里滋涅夫情妇的秘密通道
Brezhnev used it to sneak his mistress in.

964
01:05:14,979 --> 01:05:15,898
在那里吗
In where?

965
01:05:15,899 --> 01:05:16,859
在那里
In there.

966
01:05:18,019 --> 01:05:19,978
克里姆林宫
The Kremlin?

967
01:05:19,979 --> 01:05:21,978
核弹在克里姆林宫
The weapon is in the Kremlin?

968
01:05:21,979 --> 01:05:23,979
那是他们唯一不会检查的地方
It's the one place they wouldn't look.

969
01:05:40,979 --> 01:05:43,979
天啊 你能让它保暖吗
Jesus.Do you mind keeping it warm?

970
01:05:57,979 --> 01:06:01,058
你不知道你所做造成了多大破坏
You have no idea the damage you've done.

971
01:06:01,059 --> 01:06:04,058
你居然把自己人关了32年
You kept one of our own locked up for 32 years.

972
01:06:04,059 --> 01:06:05,179
我要让世界维持和平
I have kept the world safe.

973
01:06:05,939 --> 01:06:07,018
如果核武落入不法份子手中呢
If that weapon falls into the wrong hands.

974
01:06:07,019 --> 01:06:08,899
武器
The weapon?

975
01:06:09,979 --> 01:06:13,059
你真是什么都不懂
You haven't the slightest idea.

976
01:06:19,019 --> 01:06:22,978
你要马上联系摩西 他不知道是陷阱
You must let me call Moses. He doesn't know what he's walking into.

977
01:06:22,979 --> 01:06:27,058
你已经有过这机会的 都结束了
You've had your chance. It's over.

978
01:06:27,059 --> 01:06:29,099
我很抱歉 维多利亚
I'm sorry, Victoria.

979
01:06:35,099 --> 01:06:37,939
去你妈的抱歉
sorry, my ass.

980
01:06:38,979 --> 01:06:41,058
他们说你是这里的传奇
They say you're a legend around here.

981
01:06:41,059 --> 01:06:42,019
但是 我...
I've...

982
01:06:43,099 --> 01:06:45,059
我从没有听说过
I've never heard of you.

983
01:06:45,939 --> 01:06:48,939
一定要说些我以前的事
Must have been a bit before my time.

984
01:06:54,099 --> 01:06:56,859
现在听说过我了吧
You've heard of me now.

985
01:06:59,059 --> 01:07:03,098
他们怎么检测不到核弹的幅射呢
How is it possible they never picked up the radiation signature from that bomb?

986
01:07:03,099 --> 01:07:05,059
这个问题很好
That's the million dollar question.

987
01:07:06,979 --> 01:07:10,018
嘿 伙计 这是新的
Hey, gang. This is new.

988
01:07:10,019 --> 01:07:12,019
墙的后面是什么呢
What do you think is behind that wall?

989
01:07:14,099 --> 01:07:16,099
应该是俄国人
I think Russians.

990
01:07:39,059 --> 01:07:41,978
要是有人发现这个洞 我们就死定了
If anybody sees that hole, we're dead.

991
01:07:41,979 --> 01:07:43,938
我需要你解除核武装置
I'm gonna need you to help me to disarm the weapon.

992
01:07:43,939 --> 01:07:45,859
要有人在外面把风
Somebody's gotta guard the door.

993
01:07:46,939 --> 01:07:47,898
不
No.

994
01:07:47,899 --> 01:07:48,859
但是
But...

995
01:07:50,099 --> 01:07:51,019
你需要这个
You'll need this.

996
01:07:57,059 --> 01:07:58,099
主席
COMRADE GENERAL

997
01:07:58,899 --> 01:08:01,099
这是20分钟前被带进红场的
THIS IS RED SQUARE 20 MINUTES AGO

998
01:08:01,860 --> 01:08:04,099
检查建筑物 军队戒备
SECURITY SWEEP THE BUILDING, GET THE ARMY NOW

999
01:08:04,899 --> 01:08:05,498
再来一次  是的
One more time.

1000
01:08:10,979 --> 01:08:12,978
很好 是什么意思
Great. What does that mean?

1001
01:08:12,979 --> 01:08:15,018
瓦斯外泄 工作人员很快就会来了
"Gas leak. Maintenance is coming."

1002
01:08:15,019 --> 01:08:16,098
很好 然后他们就会走
Good. And then they'll move on.

1003
01:08:16,099 --> 01:08:17,059
如果不走呢
What if they don't?

1004
01:08:17,899 --> 01:08:18,059
想要支枪吗
Want a gun?

1005
01:08:18,060 --> 01:08:18,978
好啊
Yes.

1006
01:08:18,979 --> 01:08:20,098
不能拿枪
No gun.

1007
01:08:20,099 --> 01:08:22,018
别动
Just don't move.

1008
01:08:22,019 --> 01:08:23,059
你是安全警卫
You're a security guard.

1009
01:08:24,059 --> 01:08:26,019
别笑 你不能笑
Don't smile. You can't smile.

1010
01:08:29,059 --> 01:08:31,899
只要不离开岗位就行了 好吗
You never leave your post. Okay?

1011
01:08:33,019 --> 01:08:34,899
很好
Nice.

1012
01:08:47,019 --> 01:08:49,018
两个摄影头 这里和这里
2 shots, here and here.

1013
01:08:49,019 --> 01:08:51,098
把他拖进去 来一个杀一个
Drag the body in there and repeat as necessay.

1014
01:08:51,099 --> 01:08:52,019
不安全吗
No safety.

1015
01:08:52,860 --> 01:08:53,979
不安全
No safety.

1016
01:09:07,979 --> 01:09:10,979
法兰克 我真不喜欢克里姆林宫
Frank, I don't like the Kremlin so much.

1017
01:09:11,899 --> 01:09:15,939
不过我喜欢在底下
And I like being underneath it even less.

1018
01:09:28,899 --> 01:09:29,939
到了
Here we are.

1019
01:09:31,939 --> 01:09:35,019
太好了 没什么变化
That's great. It's just like yesterday.

1020
01:09:36,059 --> 01:09:38,979
这是我的旧铁撬 你们看
There's my crow bar. Look at this.

1021
01:09:40,099 --> 01:09:42,058
这里
There.

1022
01:09:42,059 --> 01:09:43,978
大家来看
Hey, look, chaps.

1023
01:09:43,979 --> 01:09:46,018
我的旧烟斗 我记得放在...
That's my old pipe. I knew I'd left it somewhere.

1024
01:09:46,019 --> 01:09:49,058
我妻子1969年给我的结婚礼物
My dear wife bought this for me in 1969. It was our wedding anniversay.

1025
01:09:49,059 --> 01:09:50,058
喔 对了
Oh yes!

1026
01:09:50,059 --> 01:09:54,899
这个是"暗影行动"
This is Nightshade, by the way.

1027
01:09:59,939 --> 01:10:01,099
这里
There.

1028
01:10:02,099 --> 01:10:03,059
那是什么
Is that...?

1029
01:10:03,899 --> 01:10:05,098
红色水银柱
That's Red Mercuy.

1030
01:10:05,099 --> 01:10:07,098
红色水银柱
Red Mercuy?

1031
01:10:07,099 --> 01:10:10,018
我们冷战就是为了这个在拼命
We were always told it was a Cold War myth.

1032
01:10:10,019 --> 01:10:11,978
是 他们说制造不出来 但我做到了
Yes, they said it couldn't be done, but I did it.

1033
01:10:11,979 --> 01:10:13,099
如果这是真的红色水银柱
If that's Red Mercuy...

1034
01:10:13,939 --> 01:10:16,938
我们就可以用背包带着走
you can zip it up in a backpack and take it on the White House tour.

1035
01:10:16,939 --> 01:10:18,098
然后在不被发现的状况毁掉白宫
It's undetectable.

1036
01:10:18,099 --> 01:10:21,018
没有幅射 没有预兆
No signature. No fallout.

1037
01:10:21,019 --> 01:10:24,938
这是种需要能量平衡的武器
This weapon will entirely change the balance of international power...

1038
01:10:24,939 --> 01:10:25,979
就像...
overnight. Just like that.

1039
01:10:27,059 --> 01:10:29,098
我们都会死的
We're all gonna die.

1040
01:10:29,099 --> 01:10:30,939
跪下
On your knees.

1041
01:10:33,899 --> 01:10:35,019
卡嘉
Katia.

1042
01:10:35,939 --> 01:10:37,979
任何政府都不该拥有这武器
No government should have this weapon.

1043
01:10:38,899 --> 01:10:41,019
你们不能 我们也不能
Not yours. And not mine.

1044
01:10:41,899 --> 01:10:43,059
我有命令
I have orders.

1045
01:10:44,099 --> 01:10:47,098
这不是命令的事 是有关对与错的事
This isn't about orders. This is about right and wrong.

1046
01:10:47,099 --> 01:10:48,939
别过来
Don't.

1047
01:10:50,939 --> 01:10:53,098
你真的到美国来看我吗
Did you really come to see me in the States?

1048
01:10:53,099 --> 01:10:54,899
是的
Yes.

1049
01:10:55,860 --> 01:10:58,859
我屋子外的花是什么颜色
What color were the flowers outside my house?

1050
01:11:05,099 --> 01:11:07,059
黄色
Yellow.

1051
01:11:18,099 --> 01:11:21,059
我注意到你一直背靠着墙
I notice you are still holding up the wall.

1052
01:11:23,979 --> 01:11:27,859
瓦斯外泄 工作人员很快就会来了
Gas Leak, maintenance is coming

1053
01:11:29,939 --> 01:11:31,899
我叫帕夏
I am Pasha.

1054
01:11:33,019 --> 01:11:37,899
晚点去喝一杯吧
You want to get a drink later?

1055
01:11:40,059 --> 01:11:41,939
什么
Yes?

1056
01:11:45,059 --> 01:11:49,099
我想你也注意到我了
I thought perhaps you noticed me too!

1057
01:12:02,099 --> 01:12:04,939
这是在干什么
What in the name of? Hey!

1058
01:12:06,939 --> 01:12:08,978
你为什么吻这个家伙
What are you doing kissing this guy?

1059
01:12:08,979 --> 01:12:10,018
我不想杀他啊
I didn't wanna kill him.

1060
01:12:10,019 --> 01:12:12,098
这是什么狗屁逻辑
What kinda stupid logic is that?

1061
01:12:12,099 --> 01:12:14,018
她在这里做什么
What in the Sam Hill is she doing here?

1062
01:12:14,019 --> 01:12:15,178
她跟我们一起工作
She's working with us again.

1063
01:12:15,939 --> 01:12:17,098
就她吗
Like heck she is.

1064
01:12:17,099 --> 01:12:18,058
为什么吻那个家伙
Why were you kissing that guy?

1065
01:12:18,059 --> 01:12:22,019
孩子 不管发生什么事 你们都要留在克里姆林宫里
Kids, what happens in the Kremlin stays in the Kremlin.

1066
01:12:24,099 --> 01:12:27,859
你要对我解释一下
You are gonna have to explain this to me.

1067
01:12:49,059 --> 01:12:51,018
干杯
Hey, Comrades!

1068
01:12:51,019 --> 01:12:52,059
为我们的成功
Here's to more success.

1069
01:12:52,899 --> 01:12:53,399
成功
Success.

1070
01:12:53,939 --> 01:12:54,938
拯救世界
And saving the world!

1071
01:12:54,939 --> 01:13:00,859
拯救全世界
Saving the world!

1072
01:13:05,899 --> 01:13:08,058
我要接个电话 等一下回来
I got this. Right back.

1073
01:13:08,059 --> 01:13:09,059
嘿
Hey.

1074
01:13:09,860 --> 01:13:10,898
你在哪里
Where are you?

1075
01:13:10,899 --> 01:13:11,978
莫斯科
Moscow.

1076
01:13:11,979 --> 01:13:13,059
他不是疯子 法兰克
He's a nutter, Francis.

1077
01:13:13,939 --> 01:13:16,098
MI6关他不是因为他制造武器
MI6 didn't lock him up because he created the weapon...

1078
01:13:16,099 --> 01:13:17,939
因为他想要造反
but because he wants to see it go off.

1079
01:13:23,019 --> 01:13:25,098
哈罗 法兰克
Hello, Frank.

1080
01:13:25,099 --> 01:13:27,978
是维多利亚 对吗
That was Victoria, wasn't it?

1081
01:13:27,979 --> 01:13:30,098
说我是怪物之类的
Telling you that I was some sort of a monster...

1082
01:13:30,099 --> 01:13:34,019
想要摧毁苏维埃帝国
who once wanted to destroy the Soviet empire.

1083
01:13:34,899 --> 01:13:37,979
是 慢慢地
Yeah. Vey slowly.

1084
01:13:39,099 --> 01:13:41,979
这就对了
That's it. Good boy.

1085
01:13:46,939 --> 01:13:50,098
走前面
Good. In you go.

1086
01:13:50,099 --> 01:13:52,098
马文
Marvin...

1087
01:13:52,099 --> 01:13:54,979
放下武器
Guns down.

1088
01:14:01,059 --> 01:14:04,899
放下武器 慢慢转身
Weapons down. Vey slowly.

1089
01:14:05,899 --> 01:14:08,058
你一开始就在计划了 是吧
You planted the thing on WikiLeaks.

1090
01:14:08,059 --> 01:14:11,099
对 这是从警卫那里弄来的电话
Yes, it was a cell phone taken from a guard.

1091
01:14:11,939 --> 01:14:14,019
我恨不得就在MI6里面报仇
I was just itching to get my revenge on MI6.

1092
01:14:14,939 --> 01:14:18,018
法兰克 你能找到"青蛙" 只能说你运气好
Frank, you were absolutely marvelous the way you found The Frog.

1093
01:14:18,019 --> 01:14:19,339
别人都找不到
No one else could have found him.

1094
01:14:19,899 --> 01:14:20,939
杰克
Jack?

1095
01:14:22,059 --> 01:14:26,018
抱歉 法兰克 看来我要启动炸弹了
sorry, Frank, I made a deal already with Mr. Gordon for Red Mercuy.

1096
01:14:26,019 --> 01:14:27,058
做得好 贝利
Well done, Bailey.

1097
01:14:27,059 --> 01:14:28,059
谢谢
Thanks.

1098
01:14:28,899 --> 01:14:29,978
很高兴又见面了
Nice to see you again.

1099
01:14:29,979 --> 01:14:31,019
把枪收起来
Pick up the guns.

1100
01:14:31,979 --> 01:14:35,059
你的国家感谢你的牺牲
Your county appreciates your sacrifice.

1101
01:14:36,019 --> 01:14:38,059
你的时辰到了
But your time's up.

1102
01:14:38,899 --> 01:14:40,099
我们走
Let's go.

1103
01:14:41,899 --> 01:14:43,018
是时候了 贝利
It's time, Bailey.

1104
01:14:43,019 --> 01:14:44,939
对 是时候了
Yes, it is time.

1105
01:14:46,939 --> 01:14:51,098
很有趣 两名美国特工变成恐怖份子
Vey Interesting. Rogue American agents turned nuclear terrorists...

1106
01:14:51,099 --> 01:14:54,018
还杀了俄国官员
kill top Russian officer.

1107
01:14:54,019 --> 01:14:55,978
这可不太好
Not good.

1108
01:14:55,979 --> 01:14:59,058
再见 法兰克 再见 马文
So long, Frank. So long, Marvin.

1109
01:14:59,059 --> 01:15:01,859
来 跟我来
Come on, boys, let's go.

1110
01:15:05,979 --> 01:15:07,979
放松
Easy.

1111
01:15:39,979 --> 01:15:42,019
让我来开门
Please, let me take that from you.

1112
01:15:42,939 --> 01:15:45,058
我以为会在伦敦听到任务报告
I thought we were doing the debriefing in London.

1113
01:15:45,059 --> 01:15:46,018
是的
We were.

1114
01:15:46,019 --> 01:15:49,098
但你目前还不安全 我们要去科罗拉多
But since you're such a sick, twisted bastard, you're going to Colorado.

1115
01:15:49,099 --> 01:15:52,098
那里有个秘密基地 大约离地一英里
There's a secret facility there, about a mile underground...

1116
01:15:52,099 --> 01:15:53,978
你将留在那里渡过你的余生
where you will spend your remaining years...

1117
01:15:53,979 --> 01:15:57,058
包括你头脑里的一切知识
having evey bit of knowledge plucked from that giant head of yours.

1118
01:15:57,059 --> 01:15:58,059
真的吗
Really?

1119
01:15:58,939 --> 01:16:02,098
有趣的是 接下来的32年
Frankly, it will make your last 32 years...

1120
01:16:02,099 --> 01:16:04,059
就好像在加勒比海渡假一样
seem like a vacation in the Caribbean.

1121
01:16:05,939 --> 01:16:06,899
把他铐起来
Cuff him.

1122
01:16:09,059 --> 01:16:10,059
知道了
I say.

1123
01:16:11,099 --> 01:16:12,059
好吧 好吧
Well, well.

1124
01:16:15,939 --> 01:16:17,898
我打赌你一定没想到 是吗 老头？
Bet you didn't see that coming. Did you, old man?

1125
01:16:17,899 --> 01:16:17,901


1126
01:16:17,902 --> 01:16:20,098
我只能说我的确没有想到 很好
I must say, I didn't. Jolly good.

1127
01:16:20,099 --> 01:16:20,979
你先请
After you.

1128
01:16:21,939 --> 01:16:23,299
先生们 谢谢 早安
Thank you.Good morning, gentlemen.

1129
01:16:44,860 --> 01:16:45,898
他说什么
What did he say?

1130
01:16:45,899 --> 01:16:46,399
预备
Ready.

1131
01:16:47,099 --> 01:16:49,018
想想办法 想想办法
Do something. Do something.

1132
01:16:49,019 --> 01:16:50,018
我爱你
I love you.

1133
01:16:50,019 --> 01:16:52,058
至少韩不会先杀死我们
At least Han didn't get us first.

1134
01:16:52,059 --> 01:16:54,099
