关掉 用什么关 气功
Shut Yeah. With what? Acupressure?

1326
01:32:24,939 --> 01:32:25,898
我怎么知道
I don't know.

1327
01:32:25,899 --> 01:32:27,938
为什么是我的责任
Why is it my responsibility?

1328
01:32:27,939 --> 01:32:30,058
做点什么
Just do something.

1329
01:32:30,059 --> 01:32:32,899
我的化学很烂
With my Mr. Chemisty set?

1330
01:32:33,899 --> 01:32:35,098
我不知道我在干什么
I don't know what I'm doing.

1331
01:32:35,099 --> 01:32:36,298
你要我按这个按钮吗
You want me to push a button?

1332
01:32:36,860 --> 01:32:39,019
贝利不见了 炸弹计时中
Bailey's loose and the bomb's ticking.

1333
01:32:43,899 --> 01:32:45,098
对不起 女士
Wait. Excuse me, ma'am.

1334
01:32:45,099 --> 01:32:46,899
你好 我有预约
Hello, I have an appointment.

1335
01:32:49,979 --> 01:32:50,899
有枪
Gun!

1336
01:33:15,979 --> 01:33:17,019
把炸弹拿远一点
Get that bomb outta here.

1337
01:33:22,939 --> 01:33:23,978
放下 亲爱的  对了
Drop it now, darling. That's right.

1338
01:33:23,979 --> 01:33:24,859
我的枪
My gun!

1339
01:33:31,899 --> 01:33:33,139
快按钮 下楼
Press the button. Ground floor.

1340
01:33:33,899 --> 01:33:34,979
马文 快点
Marvin, let's go!

1341
01:33:40,899 --> 01:33:41,859
很好玩
Jolly good show.

1342
01:33:48,939 --> 01:33:49,439
去你奶奶的
Bollocks.

1343
01:33:54,939 --> 01:33:57,058
你会开这荒唐的东西吗
You really drive this ridiculous thing?

1344
01:33:57,059 --> 01:33:58,059
你会射击吗
Can you shoot?

1345
01:34:04,899 --> 01:34:06,059
我需要指引 法兰克
We need eyes, Francis.

1346
01:34:19,059 --> 01:34:20,939
来吧 法兰克 剩40分钟
Come on, Frank. 40 minutes.

1347
01:34:29,979 --> 01:34:31,058
怎么样了
How ya doin' back there?

1348
01:34:31,059 --> 01:34:32,939
我现在不能说话
I can't talk to you right now.

1349
01:34:36,059 --> 01:34:36,979
如何呢
How is it?

1350
01:34:37,939 --> 01:34:38,859
非常好
It's fine.

1351
01:34:42,019 --> 01:34:42,979
操
Shit!

1352
01:34:46,979 --> 01:34:48,019
秀给我看看
Show me something.

1353
01:35:13,979 --> 01:35:14,898
维多利亚
Victoria...

1354
01:35:14,899 --> 01:35:17,058
我看见了 贝利正要去机场的路上
I got eyes on. Bailey's heading for the M4.

1355
01:35:17,059 --> 01:35:17,939
明白
Got it.

1356
01:35:20,099 --> 01:35:20,979
知道了
Got it!

1357
01:35:22,059 --> 01:35:26,018
这条剪了会停止或者爆炸
This one should stop it and this one should detonate it.

1358
01:35:26,019 --> 01:35:26,979
各50%的机率
It's fifty fifty.

1359
01:35:29,979 --> 01:35:30,899
等等
Wait!

1360
01:35:32,979 --> 01:35:33,979
不对劲
That's weird.

1361
01:35:34,939 --> 01:35:36,499
你知道自己在做什么吗
Do you have any idea what you're doing?

1362
01:35:38,899 --> 01:35:39,399
等等
Wait, wait!

1363
01:35:39,939 --> 01:35:42,058
停止剪那些电线
Stop cutting wires!

1364
01:35:42,059 --> 01:35:43,979
我知道我们都要死了
I knew we were gonna die!

1365
01:35:46,099 --> 01:35:47,938
准备好杀掉这贱人了吗
Ready to kill this son of a bitch?

1366
01:35:47,939 --> 01:35:49,059
随时准备着
Abso bloody lutely.

1367
01:35:52,019 --> 01:35:52,899
妈的
Damn it!

1368
01:35:57,899 --> 01:35:58,399
麻烦了
Trouble.

1369
01:35:59,019 --> 01:35:59,978
马文
Marvin!

1370
01:35:59,979 --> 01:36:02,938
需要两脚采踏板 两手握控制器
It's 2 pedals and 2 sticks.

1371
01:36:02,939 --> 01:36:03,899
好的
Okay.

1372
01:36:39,899 --> 01:36:42,018
见鬼 追丢了 他朝机场去了
Damn it! We missed him. He's going into the airport.

1373
01:36:42,019 --> 01:36:43,058
抓住他
Go get him!

1374
01:36:43,059 --> 01:36:44,098
你在哪里
Where are you?

1375
01:36:44,099 --> 01:36:45,019
有些麻烦事
In trouble.

1376
01:36:45,860 --> 01:36:48,099
飞回去 你在禁飞区中
Turn back! You are in restricted airspace.

1377
01:36:48,899 --> 01:36:49,099
我们马上要在空中爆炸了
They're gonna blow us outta the sky.

1378
01:36:49,899 --> 01:36:50,938
我一点也不担心
I wouldn't wory about that.

1379
01:36:50,939 --> 01:36:52,018
把引擎关掉
The engine's shutting down.

1380
01:36:52,019 --> 01:36:54,098
求救 求救
Mayday! Mayday!

1381
01:36:54,099 --> 01:36:55,019
法兰克!
Frank!

1382
01:36:56,099 --> 01:36:58,058
我知道我们要死了
I knew we were gonna die!

1383
01:36:58,059 --> 01:36:59,018
这是最后的警告
This is your last warning!

1384
01:36:59,019 --> 01:37:02,019
拜托告诉我 你们不是带了 大规模杀伤力武器坠落
Please, tell me you're not crashing with a weapon of mass destruction.

1385
01:37:05,059 --> 01:37:06,939
不 法兰克 不要啊
No, Frank, no.

1386
01:37:12,899 --> 01:37:13,899
天啊
Oh God.

1387
01:37:26,019 --> 01:37:27,059
你还好吗
You okay back there?

1388
01:37:27,899 --> 01:37:30,938
如果正确着陆多好 法兰克
It wasn't exactly a three point landing, Frank.

1389
01:37:30,939 --> 01:37:31,939
炸弹怎么样了
How's the bomb doing?

1390
01:37:35,019 --> 01:37:36,899
我无法停止它
I can't stop it.

1391
01:37:49,939 --> 01:37:51,059
我们要离开这里
We gotta get it outta here.

1392
01:37:52,979 --> 01:37:53,938
嘿
Hey!

1393
01:37:53,939 --> 01:37:55,899
下车
Get outta the car.

1394
01:38:07,019 --> 01:38:08,019
你好 法兰克
Hello, Frank.

1395
01:38:08,899 --> 01:38:09,979
欢迎登机
Welcome aboard.

1396
01:38:12,939 --> 01:38:14,378
你一直是个好士兵 不是吗
Always the good soldier, aren't you?

1397
01:38:16,099 --> 01:38:18,018
僵持状态
Stalemate.

1398
01:38:18,019 --> 01:38:20,058
你要如何救他出去
How will you take him out...

1399
01:38:20,059 --> 01:38:21,939
而不会打到她
and not shoot her first?

1400
01:38:23,099 --> 01:38:25,059
法兰克 没事的
Frank, it's okay.

1401
01:38:26,059 --> 01:38:28,859
你可以开枪 没事的
You can shoot. It's okay.

1402
01:38:29,860 --> 01:38:32,019
放下枪
Put the gun down.

1403
01:38:33,059 --> 01:38:34,059
放下枪
Put the gun down!

1404
01:38:36,899 --> 01:38:37,859
把枪扔一边
Drop the gun!

1405
01:38:40,899 --> 01:38:43,979
放下枪 法兰克
Put the gun down, Frankie.

1406
01:38:45,059 --> 01:38:46,099
谢谢配合
Thank you.

1407
01:38:47,979 --> 01:38:48,979
很聪明
Pretty smart.

1408
01:38:50,059 --> 01:38:52,939
爱能征服一切啊
So love does conquer all.

1409
01:38:54,019 --> 01:38:55,899
你到那边去
Go to your golden warrior.

1410
01:38:58,099 --> 01:38:59,099
好女孩
That's a good girl.

1411
01:39:05,059 --> 01:39:06,098
过来
Come here.

1412
01:39:06,099 --> 01:39:08,979
真感人啊
It's so sweet.

1413
01:39:10,099 --> 01:39:14,059
现在离开飞机 带着那个炸弹
Now leave the plane. Take Nightshade with you.

1414
01:39:16,059 --> 01:39:17,019
再见了 法兰克
Bye, Frank.

1415
01:39:19,899 --> 01:39:20,939
做个好梦
Sweet dreams.

1416
01:39:36,099 --> 01:39:37,899
你为什么不开枪
Why didn't you just shoot me?

1417
01:39:56,059 --> 01:39:57,018
怎么了
What happened?

1418
01:39:57,019 --> 01:39:58,059
我不能停止倒数
I couldn't disarm it.

1419
01:40:06,099 --> 01:40:07,899
喔 见鬼
Crap.

1420
01:40:09,899 --> 01:40:10,399
马文
Marvin...

1421
01:40:11,019 --> 01:40:12,059
快要爆炸了吗
it's going to detonate?

1422
01:40:12,979 --> 01:40:14,018
是的
Yeah.

1423
01:40:14,019 --> 01:40:15,059
抱着我
Put your arms around me.

1424
01:40:37,939 --> 01:40:38,939
啊
Oh...

1425
01:40:40,019 --> 01:40:41,899
我怎么没预料到这个
I didn't see that one coming.

1426
01:41:00,059 --> 01:41:02,059
这种事不是每天都看得到喔
There's something you don't see evey day.

1427
01:41:07,899 --> 01:41:09,138
你把炸弹放到飞机上了
You put the bomb on the plane.

1428
01:41:12,979 --> 01:41:16,018
而你提都不提一下
And you didn't think to mention that?

1429
01:41:16,019 --> 01:41:18,058
你炸毁了我的飞机
You blew up my plane.

1430
01:41:18,059 --> 01:41:18,978
抱歉
sorry.

1431
01:41:18,979 --> 01:41:22,059
我错了 所以我们死期还未到嘛
I was wrong? So we're not even gonna die?

1432
01:41:22,939 --> 01:41:23,859
还没到
Not yet.

1433
01:41:25,019 --> 01:41:27,058
我甚至开始喜欢你了
I was actually starting to like you.

1434
01:41:27,059 --> 01:41:29,018
我也许不想杀你了
I was even thinking about not killing you.

1435
01:41:29,019 --> 01:41:31,098
就在你试着拯救全世界时
This is what happens when you Ty to save the world.

1436
01:41:31,099 --> 01:41:33,938
你不能计较这些
You can't put a price on these things.

1437
01:41:33,939 --> 01:41:38,058
你欠我 三千万的飞机 和 让我不杀你的二千万
You owe me 30 mil for the plane. And 20 for not killing you.

1438
01:41:38,059 --> 01:41:40,899
你已经死了 摩西
You're a dead man, Moses.

1439
01:41:42,979 --> 01:41:43,939
谢谢你的帮助
Thanks for your help.

1440
01:41:45,939 --> 01:41:46,859
真的
Really.

1441
01:41:49,059 --> 01:41:50,059
你认为他是认真的
You think he means it?

1442
01:41:50,939 --> 01:41:51,978
不 他是个好家伙
Nah, he's a nice guy.

1443
01:41:51,979 --> 01:41:53,058
我说真的 法兰克
I mean it, Frank!

1444
01:41:53,059 --> 01:41:54,019
好吧
All right.

1445
01:41:59,099 --> 01:42:00,979
他们做得对
They're going to be right as rain.

1446
01:42:03,019 --> 01:42:06,059
他寻求他的精神慰藉
He made the run to emotional safety.

1447
01:42:10,899 --> 01:42:11,859
所以
So...

1448
01:42:12,899 --> 01:42:14,939
我听说在加拉加斯有份工作
I did hear about this job in Caracas.

1449
01:42:16,099 --> 01:42:17,859
然后呢
And?

1450
01:42:31,059 --> 01:42:33,019
不要看我 她是你的女朋友
Don't look at me. She's your girlfriend.

1451
01:42:39,019 --> 01:42:39,939
走吧
Come on.
